in_2533969\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xxw1665702741737.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xxw1665702741737.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xxw1665702741737.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xxw1665702741737\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Distributed Client/Server Applications\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__distributed_client_server_applications_95287\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">In a desktop or client/server Uniface application, Form components run on the client to provide the user interface, and Service components run on remote servers to access databases and provide centralized processing.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__p_d29249e1_d29250e1_d29251e1\">To run remote components, Uniface uses:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__li_d14774e1_d14775e1_d14776e1\">Uniface Server running in the role of application server.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__li_d14777e1_d14778e1_d14779e1\">Uniface Router to manage the servers.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__li_d14780e1_d14781e1_d14782e1\">Network connectors to handle communication over the network.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__fig_d29252e1_d29253e1_d29254e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Remote Service and DBMS</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Diagram of Remote Servers\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/remoteservicedbms.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__p_d29258e1_d29259e1_d29260e1\">Services are explicitly called or activated by client application components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xxw1665702741737__p_d29261e1_d29262e1_d29263e1\">When the Uniface Server acts as an application server, it includes the engine so that it can execute the specified service components.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533969\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533969\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Distributed Client/Server Applications Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Distributed Client/Server Applications In a desktop or client/server Uniface application, Form components run on the client to provide the user interface, and Service components run on remote servers to access databases and provide centralized processing. To run remote components, Uniface uses: Uniface Server running in the role of application server. Uniface Router to manage the servers. Network connectors to handle communication over the network. Figure 1. Remote Service and DBMS Services are explicitly called or activated by client application components. When the Uniface Server acts as an application server, it includes the engine so that it can execute the specified service components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}